room_title: Escape room "Escape from 108 Ocean Ave." by Escape Room Adventures WNY in Buffalo
room_description: This house has a dark past, but you've never been scared by spooky stories and ghost rumors. As a dare from your friends, you bravely step inside the infamous house on Ocean Ave. Suddenly the door slams shut behind you. Is this supposed to be a trick? Is the house trying to claim it's next victims?
